<title>闫学晶儿子道歉：娘的错，儿子担！</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E9%97%AB%E5%AD%A6%E6%99%B6%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A8%98%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E6%8B%85%EF%BC%81</link>
